gobblin.writer

Class MultiWriterWatermarkTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.MultiWriterWatermarkTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WatermarkTracker

    public class MultiWriterWatermarkTracker
extends Object
implements WatermarkTracker
    A helper class that tracks committed and uncommitted watermarks. Useful for implementing WatermarkAwareWriters that wrap other WatermarkAwareWriters. Note: The current implementation is not meant to be used in a high-throughput scenario (e.g. in the path of a write or a callback). See LastWatermarkTracker.
